<HEADLINE>
INDIANS CRUSH YANKEES, 11-0 
</HEADLINE>
  (sw) 
 By BUSTER OLNEY   
 c.1998 N.Y. Times News Service   
<TEXT>
<P>
   CLEVELAND _ Hideki Irabu should take some solace in the fact
