   ENTERTAINMENT/ARTS (e category)
</P>
<P>
   TV-SURFER _ ``Dateline'' is an hour documentary on a multiple
personality sexual assault case in which the attacker says he's not
responsible because an alter ego is and the victim says she didn't
want to testify against him because she's his therapist and
understands his psychological problems; plus MTV's ``Biorhythm''
looks at Tupac Shakur. (Atlanta Journal-Constitution) ETA: 6 p.m.
</P>
