   SOUND-SHOPPING _ CD reviews. (DeVault, Atlanta
Journal-Constitution) ETA 8 p.m. ET.
</P>
<P>
   GARFIELD-MONTH _ BOCA RATON, Fla. _ It wasn't your average 20th
birthday bash. But Garfield isn't your average cat. The
International Museum of Cartoon Art hosted a party and book signing
recently to kick off a two-month celebration in honor of Garfield,
the fleshy, fatigued feline that cartoonist Jim Davis brought into
the world in 1978. (Mnookin, Palm Beach Post) MOVED.
</P>
