wearing new Nikes _ so new you can almost smell the box. The laces
are untied, in the dirt, but so white, so clean they or the shoes
or both are quite obviously new. Know anything about all the stolen
shoes? he's asked. What shoes, he says. It's a statement, not a
question. (Reid, Palm Beach Post) MOVED.
