<DATE_TIME> 1998-06-22 13:22 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A0362 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u a &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-PUBLIC-EDUCATION-2TAK     06-22 0941
