<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-06-22 13:45 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A0408 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u a &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-DEEP-RESEARCH-BOS &LR;      06-22 1680
