<HEADLINE>
SLOT MACHINES ARE JUST A BUS RIDE AWAY 
</HEADLINE>
   (EDs: Photos available on Wieck database)  
 (For use by New York Times News Service clients.)  
 By JOHN MacCORMACK  
 c.1998 San Antonio Express-News  
<TEXT>
<P>
   KINDER, La. _ It's 4 a.m. on a Wednesday and the nearly vacant
