</P>
<P>
   ``Oh,'' the other woman replied, ``I thought you were talking
about a computer.''
</P>
<P>
   &UR; A LITTER OF KITTENS &LR;
</P>
<P>
   A three-year-old boy went with his dad to see a new litter of
