<P>
   WATER-BOTTLED-SEATTLE (Seattle) Move over, Talking Rain. Make
room for Northwest Rain. Or Seattle Rain. Or whatever they decide
to call it. Water managers in Seattle think there would be a strong
market for bottled water from Seattle, and they've asked the
Seattle City Council to consider footing the bill for a feasibility
study.
