</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-HEAT-DEATHS-1STLD-WRITETHRU-HNS </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
AT LEAST 10 ILLEGAL IMMIGRANTS DIE FROM HEAT 
</HEADLINE>
   (EDs: Adds dropped word in lede)  
 (For use by New York Times News Service clients.)  
 By DANE SCHILLER  
 c.1998 San Antonio Express-News  
<TEXT>
